interpretation:
The flag of Åland Islands represents the autonomy and sovereignty of this archipelago located between Sweden and Finland. This card urges you to assert your own identity and take control of your own life. It suggests that you may need to create boundaries or declare independence in order to fully express your true self.

The Åland Islands are known for their peaceful and harmonious way of life, so this card also encourages you to seek balance and harmony in your relationships and surroundings. Be open to compromise and find a way to coexist peacefully with others while still honoring your own needs and values.

Overall, the flag of Åland Islands represents a strong sense of self and the importance of asserting one's autonomy and identity. Trust yourself and your instincts, and don't be afraid to stand up for what you believe in.
